Subject: Smithee Awards
Description: The Smith-ka-teers watch bad movies throughout the year and clip the best worst parts to show our audience. 19 'B Movie' categories (Stupidest Looking Monster? Oh yeah. Acting Appropriately Stupid? Got that too) and five clips per category, the audience decides which clip gets to take home the title of best of the worst. Come for some or come for all. It's free, fun and other F adjectives!  Speakers include:Jeanette Quirk, Matthew Quirk, Amy Conlon, Kevin Hogan - Track: After Dark, Media  - Duration: 3 hours and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
